lead_paragraph: FEIN--Cecile (Katz), 95, of Boca Raton, FL and Verona, NJ died on Sunday, May 29, 2016. A funeral service will be held Thursday 12:00pm at the Bernheim Apter Kreitzman Suburban Funeral Chapel, 68 Old Short Hills Road, Livingston, NJ. 1/3
